&lt;li&gt;Operate basic laboratory and pilot-scale equipment (mixers, gloveboxes, drying tools, measurement instruments).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in cell assembly steps such as stacking, winding, ultrasonic welding, and pouch sealing after training.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct basic material characterization using tools such as microscopes, thickness gauges, viscometers, or particle size instruments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
